{
  "id": "corpus-analysis-decomposed",
  "name": {
    "en": "Corpus Completeness Analysis — Decomposed (case B)",
    "de": "Korpus-Vollständigkeitsanalyse — Zerlegt (Fall B)"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "Free-form question → planner emits sub-questions → for each sub-question run its own iFinder search and per-document evidence extraction → audit-grade report. The 'nested' completeness pattern; same primitives, search happens INSIDE the outer loop.",
    "de": "Freie Frage → Planner erzeugt Teilfragen → für jede Teilfrage eine eigene iFinder-Suche und Evidenzextraktion pro Dokument → revisionssicherer Bericht. Das 'verschachtelte' Vollständigkeitsmuster; selbe Primitive, die Suche liegt INNERHALB der äußeren Schleife."
  },
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "enabled": true,
  "config": {
    "observability": "standard",
    "persistence": "session",
    "errorHandling": "fail",
    "humanInLoop": "none",
    "maxExecutionTime": 900000,
    "maxNodes": 30,
    "maxIterations": 5,
    "allowCycles": false,
    "defaultModelId": "gemini-flash-latest"
  },
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "start",
      "type": "start",
      "name": { "en": "Pose Question", "de": "Frage stellen" },
      "position": { "x": 100, "y": 50 },
      "config": {
        "inputVariables": [
          {
            "name": "userQuestion",
            "type": "string",
            "required": true,
            "label": { "en": "Question", "de": "Frage" }
          },
          {
            "name": "topicSeeds",
            "type": "string",
            "required": false,
            "label": { "en": "Topic seeds (optional)", "de": "Themenstichwörter (optional)" }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "init",
      "type": "transform",
      "name": { "en": "Init accumulators", "de": "Akkumulatoren initialisieren" },
      "position": { "x": 100, "y": 180 },
      "config": {
        "operations": [
          { "set": "_evidence", "value": [] },
          { "set": "_corpusAll", "value": [] },
          {
            "set": "_coverage",
            "value": {
              "candidates": { "total": 0, "source": "ifinder" },
              "processed": 0,
              "skipped": [],
              "failed": [],
              "quotesChecked": 0,
              "quotesValidated": 0
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "plan-subquestions",
      "type": "query-plan",
      "name": { "en": "Decompose into sub-questions", "de": "In Teilfragen zerlegen" },
      "position": { "x": 100, "y": 320 },
      "config": {
        "questionPath": "$.data.userQuestion",
        "seedsPath": "$.data.topicSeeds",
        "outputVar": "_queryPlan",
        "maxTopics": 5,
        "maxSynonymsPerTopic": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "for-each-subquestion",
      "type": "loop",
      "name": { "en": "Per sub-question", "de": "Pro Teilfrage" },
      "position": { "x": 100, "y": 480 },
      "config": {
        "mode": "forEach",
        "array": "_queryPlan.topics",
        "maxIterations": 10,
        "body": [
          {
            "id": "search-subquestion",
            "type": "corpus-search",
            "config": {
              "queryPath": "$.data._subQuestion",
              "corpusVar": "_corpus",
              "coverageVar": "_coverage",
              "maxPerTopic": 25,
              "maxTotalDocs": 100,
              "fetchFulltext": true,
              "maxFulltextChars": 30000
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "accumulate-corpus",
            "type": "code",
            "config": {
              "code": "const prev = data._corpusAll; const prevArr = Array.isArray(prev) ? prev : (prev && Array.isArray(prev.result) ? prev.result : []); [...prevArr, ...(data._corpus || [])];",
              "outputVariable": "_corpusAllRaw",
              "timeout": 5000
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "unwrap-corpus-accumulator",
            "type": "transform",
            "config": {
              "operations": [{ "copy": "_corpusAllRaw.result", "to": "_corpusAll" }]
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "for-each-doc",
            "type": "loop",
            "config": {
              "mode": "forEach",
              "array": "_corpus",
              "maxIterations": 200,
              "body": [
                {
                  "id": "extract-evidence",
                  "type": "prompt",
                  "config": {
                    "temperature": 0.2,
                    "system": {
                      "en": "You analyse one document for one specific sub-question. Extract structured findings, ground every claim in the source, quote verbatim. The downstream validator checks every quote against the source."
                    },
                    "prompt": {
                      "en": "## Original question\n${$.data.userQuestion}\n\n## Sub-question being investigated\n{{_subQuestion}}\n\n## Document (index {{_loopIndex}} for sub-question)\nTitle: {{_loopItem.title}}\nDocId: {{_loopItem.docId}}\n\n### Content\n{{_loopItem.fulltext}}\n\n## Output (JSON only, no markdown fences)\n{\n  \"keyStatements\": [\"<statement relevant to the sub-question>\"],\n  \"entities\": [\"<named entities>\"],\n  \"position\": \"<document's position on the sub-question, or empty>\",\n  \"evidenceQuotes\": [\"<VERBATIM source quote>\"],\n  \"quotes\": [{ \"text\": \"<each VERBATIM quote, one per entry>\" }]\n}"
                    },
                    "outputVariable": "_extractionOutput",
                    "maxIterations": 1,
                    "maxTokens": 6000
                  },
                  "execution": { "timeout": 90000, "retries": 1 }
                },
                {
                  "id": "collect",
                  "type": "structured-record",
                  "config": {
                    "schemaName": "corpusAnalysis",
                    "schemaVersion": "v1",
                    "inputPath": "$.data._extractionOutput",
                    "sourcePath": "$.data._loopItem",
                    "sourceSystem": "ifinder",
                    "evidenceVar": "_evidence",
                    "iterationIndexPath": "$.data._loopIndex"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "increment-processed",
                  "type": "transform",
                  "config": {
                    "operations": [{ "increment": "_coverage.processed", "by": 1 }]
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "validate",
      "type": "quote-validator",
      "name": { "en": "Validate all quotes", "de": "Alle Zitate validieren" },
      "position": { "x": 100, "y": 700 },
      "config": {
        "evidenceVar": "_evidence",
        "coverageVar": "_coverage",
        "corpusVar": "_corpusAll",
        "maxSourceChars": 30000
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "synthesise",
      "type": "prompt",
      "name": { "en": "Synthesise across sub-questions", "de": "Über Teilfragen synthetisieren" },
      "position": { "x": 100, "y": 860 },
      "config": {
        "temperature": 0.3,
        "system": {
          "en": "You synthesise evidence collected across multiple sub-questions into a single narrative. Group findings by sub-question, then offer cross-cutting themes. Cite docIds inline. Do not add facts beyond the evidence."
        },
        "prompt": {
          "en": "## Original question\n${$.data.userQuestion}\n\n## Sub-questions\n{{#each _queryPlan.topics}}\n- {{this}}\n{{/each}}\n\n## Evidence (across all sub-questions)\n{{#each _evidence}}\n- Doc {{this.source.docId}} ({{this.source.title}}): {{this.extraction.data.position}}\n{{/each}}\n\nWrite a markdown synthesis: for each sub-question a short paragraph, then a cross-cutting ## Themes section and ## Offene Punkte."
        },
        "outputVariable": "_synthesis",
        "maxIterations": 1,
        "maxTokens": 6000
      },
      "execution": { "timeout": 60000 }
    },
    {
      "id": "compose",
      "type": "template-render",
      "name": { "en": "Render audit report", "de": "Auditbericht erzeugen" },
      "position": { "x": 100, "y": 1020 },
      "config": {
        "evidenceVar": "_evidence",
        "coverageVar": "_coverage",
        "synthesisVar": "_synthesis",
        "artifactName": "corpus-analysis-decomposed.md",
        "reportVar": "_report",
        "template": "# Korpus-Vollständigkeitsanalyse (zerlegt)\n\n## Frage\n\n{{userQuestion}}\n\n{{#if _queryPlan.topics}}\n## Teilfragen\n\n{{#each _queryPlan.topics}}\n- {{this}}\n{{/each}}\n{{/if}}\n\n## Abdeckung\n\n- **Kandidaten identifiziert (über alle Teilfragen):** {{coverage.candidates.total}}\n- **Dokumente verarbeitet:** {{coverage.processed}}\n- **Zitate geprüft:** {{coverage.quotesChecked}}\n- **Zitate validiert:** {{coverage.quotesValidated}}\n\n{{#if synthesis}}\n## Synthese\n\n{{synthesis}}\n{{/if}}\n\n{{#if evidence}}\n## Per-Dokument-Evidenz\n\n{{#each evidence}}\n### {{this.source.title}}\n\n- **DocId:** {{this.source.docId}}\n- **Status:** {{this.status}}\n- **Position:** {{this.extraction.data.position}}\n\n{{#if this.extraction.data.keyStatements}}\n**Kernaussagen:**\n{{#each this.extraction.data.keyStatements}}\n- {{this}}\n{{/each}}\n{{/if}}\n\n{{#if this.quotes}}\n**Zitate:**\n{{#each this.quotes}}\n- {{#if this.validated}}✓{{/if}}{{#if this.closestMatch}}⚠ Nicht wörtlich — nächstgelegen: \"{{this.closestMatch}}\"{{/if}}{{#if this.text}} \"{{this.text}}\"{{/if}}\n{{/each}}\n{{/if}}\n\n---\n\n{{/each}}\n{{/if}}\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "expose-output",
      "type": "transform",
      "name": {
        "en": "Expose user-facing output",
        "de": "Nutzersichtbare Ausgabe bereitstellen"
      },
      "position": { "x": 100, "y": 1120 },
      "config": {
        "operations": [{ "copy": "_report.markdown", "to": "finalReport" }]
      }
    },
    { "id": "end", "type": "end", "name": { "en": "Done", "de": "Fertig" }, "position": { "x": 100, "y": 1240 }, "config": { "outputVariables": ["finalReport"] } }
  ],
  "edges": [
    { "id": "e1", "source": "start", "target": "init" },
    { "id": "e2", "source": "init", "target": "plan-subquestions" },
    { "id": "e3", "source": "plan-subquestions", "target": "for-each-subquestion" },
    { "id": "e4", "source": "for-each-subquestion", "target": "validate" },
    { "id": "e5", "source": "validate", "target": "synthesise" },
    { "id": "e6", "source": "synthesise", "target": "compose" },
    { "id": "e7", "source": "compose", "target": "expose-output" },
    { "id": "e8", "source": "expose-output", "target": "end" }
  ],
  "allowedGroups": [],
  "chatIntegration": {
    "enabled": true,
    "passthroughResult": false,
    "primaryOutput": "finalReport",
    "outputFormat": "markdown"
  }
}
